title: 'Decent product
rating: but it feels its should not be 700 rs range. Product look like 400-500 max range.'
body: '3.0 out of 5 stars''Decent product but it feels its should not be 700 rs range. Product look like 400-500 max range. I am 5\'6" and 68 kg weight. For me M size was suggested. While buying I planned to buy L size but it was not available while the time of buying and as well as now when I am planning to return it. The only problem is it is slightly tight from armpit section. I bought this only to wear it at night sleeping time. But I usually wear loose cloth at night so this annoys me a bit in terms of fitting. If L size was available I would have replaced it immediately. Not sure I should return it or not.'
